  <body>
    <div class="container">

      <div class="row">
  
        <!-- Post Content Column -->
        <div class="col-lg-8" id="postContent">
  
          <!-- Title -->
          <h1 class="mt-4" id="postTitle">The Murder of Tupac</h1>
  
          <!-- Author -->
          <p class="lead">
            by
            <a href="#">John Doe</a>
          </p>
  
          <hr>
  
          <!-- Date/Time -->
          <p>Posted on January 1, 2019 at 12:00 PM</p>
  
          <hr>
  
          <!-- Preview Image -->
          <img class="img-fluid rounded" src="/images/tupac.jpg" alt="" id="previewImage">
  
          <hr>
  
          <!-- Post Content -->
          <p class="lead">Murdered by whom?</p>
  
          <p>Tupac was an American rapper and actor that left a profound influence on rap culture and is considered one of the greatest rappers of all time.</p>
  
          <p>Sadly, Tupac was killed by gunshot wounds when he was shot 4 times in a drive-by shooting.</p>
  
          <p>The identity of the person who murdered Tupac is still left unknown.</p>
  
          <hr>
  
          <!-- Comments Form -->
          <div class="card my-4">
            <h5 class="card-header">Leave a Comment:</h5>
            <div class="card-body">
              <form>
                <div class="form-group">
                  <textarea class="form-control" rows="3" id="commentTextArea"></textarea>
                </div>
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="commentButton">Submit</button>
              </form>
            </div>
